note over browser:
The Browser created note and adds it to notes.
The Browser clears the input element.
The Browser sends a post request with body:
{"content":"I love Helsinki!","date":"2021-11-16T11:53:23.379Z"}
end note
browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
note over server:
The server creates a new note object, and adds it to an array called notes.
Then server responds to the browser with message: "note created"
end note
server-->browser: 201
